Here's the step-by-step guide ⤵️

1. Create a free thing. The better your free thing is, the better your post will perform.

2. Set up a ManyChat automation. When a user comments on your next post, it will automatically DM them a link to your free thing.

3. Make a post about your free thing! Just hype it up and illustrate the value. If it's irresistible enough, everyone will comment and the algo will boost tf out of your post.

💎 If you want my FULL in-depth guide on how to set up and use ManyChat, just comment, "CHAT" below and I will send it over to you!
